# {{lb|en|uncountable}} [[Status]] as a trustworthy source of information, reputation for [[mastery]] or [[expertise]]; or claim to such status or reputation.
#: {{ux|en|Some thinkers regard appealing to '''authority''' as a logical fallacy; others regard it as a legitimate form of argument.}}
