#: ''{{w|New York Port '''Authority'''}}''; ''{{w|Chicago Transit '''Authority'''}}''
# {{q|uncountable}} Official [[permission]]; [[authorization|authorisation]] to act in some [[capacity]] on behalf of a ruling entity.
